title: Creamy Cajun THIS™ Isn't Pork Sausage Cassoulet with Garlic Ciabatta
description: Originating from the south of France, cassoulets are typically slow-cooked and rich stews. In this vegetarian twist on a spiced cassoulet, we're using THIS™ Isn't Pork Sausages, which are made from pea proteins with a hyper-realistic texture that tastes just like the real thing.
